    "description": "<strong>You Have 10 Seconds</strong> is a fast paced arcade platformer where you’re spawned into a level and given ten seconds to work out how to reach the exit without dying before time runs out.<br><br>There are 25 Areas which each introduce a new mechanic to the gameplay, eventually creating extremely complex and difficult levels. Master collecting keys, swimming through acid, dodging motion sensors, time traveling, swapping dimensions, and so much more to clear areas as quickly as possible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390510/extras/9777be75b2c27819076683834b0fc41f.avif?t=1687332838\" width=611 height=102 /></span><br><i>- Get a rating at the end of each Area depending on how well you performed! Steam achievements for S ranks!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390510/extras/c1e0927f2bf3f2ec44c502632ce3596f.avif?t=1687332838\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><i>- Unlock Steam achievements for completing certain challenges and finding secrets!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390510/extras/992e2d56bc7fb18cfa840b44d41187cf.avif?t=1687332838\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><i>- A gauntlet of never ending randomized levels from the main game and more, how long can you survive?</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390510/extras/09034f0aac896190b0692c31d71bfe20.avif?t=1687332838\" width=572 height=88 /></span><br><i>- Removes all transitions between worlds and menu interactions for seamless gameplay for speedrunners.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390510/extras/6da783f127691e41b36ede5aeb5801a0.avif?t=1687332838\" width=469 height=102 /></span><br><i>- Some surprises hidden away that may not be found for a long, long time.</i>",
